@startuml ShareUseCase

' Sơ đồ Use Case chi tiết cho chức năng "Quản lý Hồ sơ" và "Chia sẻ"

left to right direction

' --- Định nghĩa Actors ---
actor User

' --- Định nghĩa Use Cases ---
rectangle "Share Functions" {
    usecase UC_Share as "Share Content"
    usecase UC_SharePlan as "Share Plan"
    usecase UC_ShareRecipe as "Share Recipe"
    usecase UC_ShareAchievement as "Share Achievement"
    usecase UC_Interact as "Interact with Shared Content"

    ' Mối quan hệ
    User -- UC_Share

    UC_Share .> UC_SharePlan : <<include>>
    UC_Share .> UC_ShareRecipe : <<include>>
    UC_Share .> UC_ShareAchievement : <<include>>
    UC_Share .> UC_Interact : <<include>>
}

@enduml
